# Opening Courses – V3 only

When working on Opening Courses in this context:

- **Apply changes only to V3:** Edit `my-app/src/views/OpeningCoursesV3.vue` (and its error-boundary wrapper if needed). Do not change `OpeningCoursesV2.vue`, `Courses.vue`, or other course views for Opening Courses V3 behavior unless explicitly requested.
- **V2 is the prior snapshot:** Opening Courses V2 lives in `OpeningCoursesV2.vue` (`/courses/opening-courses-v2`, `/learn/opening-courses-v2`).

This keeps design files separate (same pattern as V1 vs V2).
